								-*-text-*-

This directory contains some library modules for system-dependent
functions.

Please note that the functions in this subsystem are probably not
portable.

Build the system-dependent library modules with `make'.


Internal library modules:
-------------------------

dirs.t           File system directory handling.
dirs.t.i         Handcoded implementation of the above.
errno.t          Accessing operator system errors.
errno.t.i        Handcoded implementation of the above.
files.t		 File handling.
files.t.i        Handcoded implementation of the above.
net.t		 Network programming.
net.t.i          Handcoded implementation of the above.
procs.t          Process handling.
procs.t.i        Handcoded implementation of the above.
sigs.t           Operating system handling.
sigs.t.i         Handcoded implementation of the above.
times.t		 Time of day handling.
times.t.i        Handcoded implementation of the above.
users.t          Accessing the user data base.
users.t.i        Handcoded implementation of the above.


Administrativa:
---------------

ChangeLog        Change list for the `crawl/internal' directory.
Makefile.am      Input file for Automake for generating Makefile.in.
Makefile.in      Input file for Autoconf for generating.
